      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DASHING FOR GOLD (5) shapes as hard to beat after winning last start over the 401m at this track in a strong 22.76. Top win latest and looms as the one to beat again. SHAKE NOT STIR (1) flew the lids with a strong early split and led throughout to score an impressive win by 4 lengths over 400m at Maitland (22.29). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Bold showing expected again. FUGENZO (8) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Star Pedro (23.18) in a Grade 5. Always well back but strong run home into the finish. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to feature again. NO SHAME (2) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
